data.title: Seattle Civil Rights and Labor History Project
data.text:
Here is a digital archive of articles published in the UW Daily and other local newspapers between 1968 and 1979 on the founding and operation of El Centro de la Raza (click the titles to read the articles).

Francesca Barajas initiated this database with help from Michael Schulze-Oechtering Casta√±eda. These articles are courtesy of the UW Daily, Seattle Times, Seattle Post-Intelligencer.
